{
  "stem": "20609.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never in my life had a wristwatch.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was against the law anyway to have-- so I had a steel Omega, the ugliest thing-- I mean, today it would be the ugliest thing in the world.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't wear it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had to keep it in the barracks hidden.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I wound up with an Omega watch, my first watch in my lifetime.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And now I've got to tell you one thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was assigned after the-- after the ghetto start loosening up, you know, there was a-- I was assigned to a youth home.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, it was individual rooms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let's say a room like this, as you see here, had maybe three-- three, six, nine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It had about 30 people in there with the-- with the beds on both sides-- three, one, two, three-- three, six, nine, 18, maybe 21 beds, right? 21 bunks.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember one time we had a kid in our barrack in this room and he was so sick he couldn't eat.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He could not swallow anything, he was just wasting away but we kept him on report.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what we did that we didn't-- what we did with his bread was we toasted it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't touch it, right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and I said to myself, I says, we knew the guy was going to guy-- die.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I says, if he dies, let him die at night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because at night, we could have grabbed the bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the daytime, the orderly would have grabbed it, the guy who was in charge of the whole floor.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He died in the daytime and we didn't see the bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I tell you one thing, what I did, and I've been thinking about that.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
